[Mucoviscidosis: Background, risk factors, diagnosis strategy, treatment 
principles].

[Article in Romanian]

Trofor A(1).

Author information:
(1)Disciplina de Pneumoftiziologie, Facutatea de MedicinÄ StomatologicÄ, 
